possibility to do target sens by sens (sens +, sens - and create the carrefour manuelly by the user in the carrefour dict)
this method permit to get a better result

------------------------------------------->(+)
|  				   (c)   				   |
|  <-------------------------------------  |(-)
|  |                                    |  |
|  |                                    |  |
|  ------------------------------------->  |(-)
|  				(c)   					   |
<-------------------------------------------(+)

(c) represnt the carrefour
(+) represent the positive sens
(-) represent the negative sens